ongmen','https://goo.gl/maps/KfaP7quhVbnrzrW99',25.031076,121.5294009,'\"{\\\"mon\\\": \\\"11:30-22\\\", \\\"tue\\\": \\\"11:30-22\\\", \\\"wed\\\": \\\"11:30-22\\\", \\\"thu\\\": \\\"11:30-22\\\", \\\"fri\\\": \\\"11:30-22\\\", \\\"sat\\\": \\\"11:30-22\\\", \\\"sun\\\": \\\"11:30-22\\\"}\"','',2,5,4,4,3,5,4,3,5,4,'yes','',NULL,0,NULL,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://www.facebook.com/pages/Angel%20Cafe/290376861423250/','https://www.instagram.com/angel__cafe__/','+886233433533','','\"[\\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/angel-cafe/outside.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/angel-cafe/seating1.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/angel-cafe/seating2.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/angel-cafe/seating3.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/angel-cafe/seating4.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/angel-cafe/seating5.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/angel-cafe/menu1.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/angel-cafe/menu2.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/angel-cafe/menu3.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/angel-cafe/menu4.jpg\\\"]\"','\"{\\\"en\\\": \\\"Trendy cafe/restaurant, modern interior, dim lighting, and lounge music. It\'s workable, but might be crowded/noisy during lunch and dinner time. There are two large worktables in the back, counter seating, and more tables near the front. Lots of power outlets, but the WiFi was very slow (at least in the front seating area). Good food, and the portion size was quite good, but a little pricey.\\\\n\\\", \\\"zh-tw\\\": \\\"時尚的餐酒館+Cafe的複合式空間，一進門先走過一個優雅的植物區，再到寬敞的座位區。室內光線柔和，搭配放鬆的音樂。這在裡可以工作，不過可能氣氛輕鬆得讓人有點想拖延，而用餐時間則可能會有些擁擠和吵雜；非尖峰時刻也偶有特意來拍照的訪客，使得整體環境顯得有些輕浮，不過大體來說，是整頓得很精緻的一個空間，想靜下來打發時間的人看起來也不少。\\\\n\\\\n後方有兩張大工作桌和幾張吧台座位，前端的座位則是一般用餐型的陳列，距離較近，且WiFi非常慢，不過不論是哪個座位都能輕易找到插座。食物很好吃，份量也很足，有些貴但在這區算是很妥當的價格帶。\\\\n\\\"}\"',NULL,NULL,NULL,'628d9306-0e8e-4ea1-83f3-c6948f2b7732'),(12,'Angle Cafe\'','台北市 ⋅ 大安區','taipei','106台北市大安區瑞安街206號','Technology Building','https://goo.gl/maps/VNLzBEAfTKJvbiaVA',25.028138720012453,121.54070750541314,'\"{\\\"mon\\\": \\\"13-22\\\", \\\"tue\\\": \\\"13-22\\\", \\\"wed\\\": \\\"13-22\\\", \\\"thu\\\": \\\"13-22\\\", \\\"fri\\\": \\\"13-22\\\", \\\"sat\\\": \\\"13-22\\\", \\\"sun\\\": \\\"13-22\\\"}\"',NULL,5,94,2,4,4,4,5,3,4,3,'yes',NULL,1,0,1,0,1,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://www.facebook.com/AngleCafe','https://www.instagram.com/anglecoffeecake/','+886227066672',NULL,'\"[\\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/angle-cafe/cake.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/angle-cafe/menu1.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/angle-cafe/menu2.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/angle-cafe/menu3.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/angle-cafe/menu4.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/angle-cafe/menu5.jpg\\\"]\"','\"{\\\"en\\\": \\\"This cafe has been on my list for a long time after a friend recommended it to me. It\'s definitely a great place to work. I arrived on a weekday afternoon and it was almost full, only one table available. Even so, it was very quiet since everyone was either working or studying. The interior is quite small, but the space is comfortable and has plenty of natural light. There\'s a good selection of drinks and cakes, I tried the oolong tea cheesecake, which was very tasty!\\\\n\\\", \\\"zh-tw\\\": \\\"朋友推薦給我的［Angle咖啡］已經在我的清單上很久了，這裏的確很適合工作。我在一個平日的午候前往，抵達時居然已經接近滿座，只剩下一個位置。儘管如此整個空間卻異常的安靜，因為大家都專注在自己的事情上⋯⋯我是說，讀書或工作。\\\\n\\\\n這裡空間偏小，但有很多舒適的座位，天氣好的時候也有豐富的自然光源照進來，我點了烏龍茶和起司蛋糕，都非常好吃！\\\\n\\\"}\"',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(13,'Arthere Cafe (上樓看看)','台北市 ⋅ 信義區','taipei','110台北市信義區忠孝東路五段165巷3弄6號','Taipei City Hall','https://goo.gl/maps/SjLL4cgdwDKk8Aat9',25.041513,121.568973,'\"{\\\"mon\\\": \\\"11:30-22:30\\\", \\\"tue\\\": \\\"11:30-22:30\\\", \\\"wed\\\": \\\"11:30-22:30\\\", \\\"thu\\\": \\\"11:30-22:30\\\", \\\"fri\\\": \\\"11:30-22:30\\\", \\\"sat\\\": \\\"11:30-22:30\\\", \\\"sun\\\": \\\"11:30-22:30\\\"}\"',NULL,5,92,4,3,3,NULL,4,3,4,3,'yes',NULL,1,0,0,1,1,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://www.facebook.com/ArthereCafe','https://www.instagram.com/arthere_cafe/','+886287871782',NULL,'\"[\\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/arthere-cafe-\\\\u4e0a\\\\u6a13\\\\u770b\\\\u770b/entrance.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/arthere-cafe-\\\\u4e0a\\\\u6a13\\\\u770b\\\\u770b/seating1.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/arthere-cafe-\\\\u4e0a\\\\u6a13\\\\u770b\\\\u770b/seating2.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/arthere-cafe-\\\\u4e0a\\\\u6a13\\\\u770b\\\\u770b/seating3.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/arthere-cafe-\\\\u4e0a\\\\u6a13\\\\u770b\\\\u770b/seating4.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/arthere-cafe-\\\\u4e0a\\\\u6a13\\\\u770b\\\\u770b/seating5.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/arthere-cafe-\\\\u4e0a\\\\u6a13\\\\u770b\\\\u770b/power.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/arthere-cafe-\\\\u4e0a\\\\u6a13\\\\u770b\\\\u770b/menu.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/arthere-cafe-\\\\u4e0a\\\\u6a13\\\\u770b\\\\u770b/drink.jpg\\\"]\"','\"{\\\"en\\\": \\\"Decent cafe to sit and work at. When I arrived after lunch it was already very busy, so I guess it\'s good to arrive early. The second floor is definitely the best place to sit. Plenty of seating areas and lots of natural light. It can be a little noisy at peak times. The food menu is quite extensive but I didn\'t try any food. Lots of drink options but no regular plain black tea (only milk tea and non-caffeine tea). That was a little disappointing. I tried the chocolate banana shake instead, which was really good though. Fast WiFi and power outlets on the floor.\\\\n\\\", \\\"zh-tw\\\": \\\"上樓看看是間功能性很強的咖啡店，幾乎是為了讀書和工作類型的人打造的。我在午餐時間過後拜訪時這裡還滿熱鬧的，所以我猜可能要早點到比較好，二樓絕對是一個很好的座位區，有很多座位和自然光，尖峰時間可能會有點吵。\\\\n\\\\n餐點的選擇很多，不過這次我沒有特別點餐，另外一點可惜的是這裡只有奶茶和無咖啡因茶，剛好和我的需要相反，讓我有點小失望。不過我試了香蕉奶昔，這也很好喝唷。\\\\n\\\"}\"',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(14,'Aura 微光咖啡','台北市 ⋅ 大安區','taipei','106台北市大安區羅斯福路三段269巷9號','Taipower Building','https://goo.gl/maps/zuzkG3p8i8RYpjN39',25.01944734964168,121.53055412771403,'\"{\\\"mon\\\": \\\"12:30-22\\\", \\\"tue\\\": \\\"12:30-22\\\", \\\"wed\\\": \\\"12:30-22\\\", \\\"thu\\\": \\\"12:30-22\\\", \\\"fri\\\": \\\"12:30-22\\\", \\\"sat\\\": \\\"12:30-22\\\", \\\"sun\\\": \\\"12:30-22\\\"}\"',NULL,5,260,3,4,4,4,2,3,3,3,'yes',NULL,1,0,0,1,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://www.facebook.com/CoffeeAura/','https://www.instagram.com/coffeeaura_official/','+886283693577','https://www.coffeeaura.com.tw/','\"[\\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/aura/seating1.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/aura/seating3.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/aura/seating2.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/aura/entrance.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/aura/outside.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/aura/drinks.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/aura/menu1.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/aura/menu2.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/aura/menu3.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/aura/menu4.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/