i/cafe-roi/seating2.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/cafe-roi/interior1.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/cafe-roi/interior2.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/cafe-roi/menu.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/cafe-roi/tea.jpg\\\"]\"','\"{\\\"en\\\": \\\"A simple cafe near Taipei Arena. The interior and furniture is fairly ordinary, but there are some nice personal touches, like paintings, magazines, and a fish tank. It\'s clean and the staff was friendly. Decent WiFi, but lacking power outlets. I saw one table near the back wall that has access to power. Nice drinks selection and the food options seem pretty good as well, so it might be a good cafe to have lunch at.\\\\n\\\", \\\"zh-tw\\\": \\\"小巨蛋附近的一家簡潔的咖啡店，裝潢和傢俱都不突出但可以看出一些個人的巧思，像是插畫、雜誌以及一個魚缸，很整潔，店員也很親切。\\\\n\\\\nWiFi很理想，插座稍微少了點，好像只有後方一個座位有插座。飲料選擇很好，食物看起來也不錯，我傍晚時在這裡待了一會兒，但我想這裡也很適合在午餐時間前來吃個便飯再上工。\\\\n\\\"}\"',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(29,'Caffè Libero','台北','taipei','No. 1, Lane 243, Jinhua Street, Da’an District, Taipei City, Taiwan 106','Dongmen','https://goo.gl/maps/mUux8Sb6QdaJAQGx6',25.030017792957942,121.5306203390667,'\"{\\\"mon\\\": \\\"11-0\\\", \\\"tue\\\": \\\"11-0\\\", \\\"wed\\\": \\\"11-0\\\", \\\"thu\\\": \\\"11-0\\\", \\\"fri\\\": \\\"11-0\\\", \\\"sat\\\": \\\"11-0\\\", \\\"sun\\\": \\\"11-0\\\"}\"',NULL,4,56,5,3,4,NULL,4,2,4,4,'yes',NULL,1,0,0,1,1,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://www.facebook.com/LiberoCoffeeBar/',NULL,'+886223567129',NULL,'\"[\\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/caffe-libero/seating1.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/caffe-libero/seating2.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/caffe-libero/seating3.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/caffe-libero/seating4.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/caffe-libero/seating5.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/caffe-libero/outside.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/caffe-libero/sign.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/caffe-libero/menu1.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/caffe-libero/menu2.jpg\\\"]\"','\"{\\\"en\\\": \\\"An interesting cafe with three different seating areas, each with its own style. There\'s a large outdoor seating area as well. I\'m not quite sure if this is a bar, restaurant, cafe, or maybe all three! The \\\\\\\"lounge\\\\\\\" room looks really cool, but it\'s not very suitable for working. The staff is friendly, there\'s good WiFi, and power outlets at some seats. It was almost empty during the late afternoon on a weekday, perhaps because the prices are quite high (200+ for a small drink) compared to some other cafes nearby.\\\\n\\\", \\\"zh-tw\\\": \\\"這是一家很有趣的咖啡店，三個不同空間各自表述，同時還有一個很寬敞的戶外空間。我不太確定這裡到底是Bar、餐廳，還是咖啡店，也許都算吧？其中的「Lounge」空間實在太帥了，儘管不太適合用來工作。\\\\n\\\\n店員都很親切，WiFi也很好，部分座位有插座，傍晚通常很空，我猜是因為價位比周邊幾處高的關係，但值得一試（200+ for 小杯飲品）\\\\n\\\"}\"',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(30,'CAT.jpg cafe','台北','taipei','No. 154, Chaozhou Street, Da’an District, Taipei City, Taiwan 106','Dongmen','https://goo.gl/maps/NHRiPxUNpMpjgKXaA',25.028361,121.528964,'\"{\\\"mon\\\": \\\"8-16\\\", \\\"tue\\\": \\\"8-16\\\", \\\"wed\\\": \\\"8-16\\\", \\\"thu\\\": \\\"8-16\\\", \\\"fri\\\": \\\"8-16\\\", \\\"sat\\\": \\\"8-16\\\", \\\"sun\\\": \\\"8-16\\\"}\"',NULL,4,30,3,3,4,NULL,4,5,4,3,'yes',NULL,1,0,0,NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://www.facebook.com/cat.jpg.cafe','https://www.instagram.com/cat.jpgcafe/','+886233652865',NULL,'\"[\\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/catjpg-cafe/outside.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/catjpg-cafe/counter.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/catjpg-cafe/worktable.jpg\\\",