ps://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/dreamers-coffee-roasters-guangfu/seating.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/dreamers-coffee-roasters-guangfu/power.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/dreamers-coffee-roasters-guangfu/interior.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/dreamers-coffee-roasters-guangfu/menu.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/dreamers-coffee-roasters-guangfu/tea.jpg\\\"]\"','\"{\\\"en\\\": \\\"There are several Dreamers Coffee locations in Taipei, but this one near Sun Yat-Sen Memorial Hall is my favorite. They open at 7 every day, so it\'s a great place to work in the mornings, especially since it usually gets very busy after lunch. Good natural light thanks to the large windows all around. The large worktable (with power outlets) is great to work from. There are also power outlets by all the smaller tables. The WiFi works for basic browsing, but it\'s not super fast. Cheap drinks, but tea selection is slightly lacking in my opinion.\\\\n\\\", \\\"zh-tw\\\": \\\"在台北有不少家Dreamers，在國父紀念館附近的這家是我的首選。它位置優秀，非常方便前往，尤其是早上七點開始營業這點真的非常適合早鳥們，一大清早總是特別清幽，到中午才會真正忙起來。\\\\n\\\\nDreamers國父紀念館店有大片落地窗，陽光得以自然地灑落在室內，有著許多插座的大桌非常適合辦公，當然周邊的小桌也都少不了插座。 WiFi尚可，飲料價位便宜，只是比較少茶類可以選。\\\\n\\\"}\"',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(49,'Dreamers - Neihu (內湖店)','台北','taipei','No. 11號, Alley 22, Lane 513, Ruiguang Road, Neihu District, Taipei City, 114','Xihu','https://g.page/DreamersCoffeeRoastersNeihu?share',25.080041722646985,121.56883018814672,'\"{\\\"mon\\\": \\\"7-22\\\", \\\"tue\\\": \\\"7-22\\\", \\\"wed\\\": \\\"7-22\\\", \\\"thu\\\": \\\"7-22\\\", \\\"fri\\\": \\\"7-22\\\", \\\"sat\\\": \\\"7-22\\\", \\\"sun\\\": \\\"7-22\\\"}\"',NULL,1,2,5,3,4,4,3,4,5,1,'yes',NULL,1,0,1,0,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://www.facebook.com/DreamersCoffeeRoasters','https://www.instagram.com/dreamerscoffee_tw/','+886227970819',NULL,'\"[\\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/dreamers-coffee-roasters-neihu/seating1.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/dreamers-coffee-roasters-neihu/seating3.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/dreamers-coffee-roasters-neihu/seating2.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/dreamers-coffee-roasters-neihu/seating5.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/dreamers-coffee-roasters-neihu/seating4.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/dreamers-coffee-roasters-neihu/interior1.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/dreamers-coffee-roasters-neihu/interior2.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/dreamers-coffee-roasters-neihu/entrance.jpg\\\"]\"','\"{\\\"en\\\": \\\"This Dreamers location actually feels more like a co-working space than a cafe. Huge spacious interior, with lots of seating areas across two floors. I especially like the counter seats on the second floor overlooking the first floor. As with other Dreamers locations, there are plenty of food and drink options available.\\\\n\\\\nThere are some unfortunate downsides though. The WiFi was basically unusable (extremely slow and unstable) and the restroom facilities are very basic (no soap provided). It\'s a shame, if it wasn\'t for these things, this place has the potential to be one of the best work spots in Taipei.\\\\n\\\", \\\"zh-tw\\\": \\\"我常常覺得Dreamers比較像共享辦公室而不是Cafe，幾乎所有分店都有非常寬敞的室內空間以及各種類型的座位供挑選，我特別喜歡坐在二樓靠欄杆的吧檯桌鳥瞰一樓，視野絕佳。和其他分店一樣，內湖店也有許多餐點和飲料。\\\\n\\\\n可惜的是還是有些不可避的小缺點，WiFi基本上不堪用(非常慢且不穩定)，廁所比較簡單(沒有洗手乳或肥皂)。如果沒有這些，Dreamers 內湖店基本上很有機會角逐台北工作咖啡廳的冠軍。\\\\n\\\"}\"',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(50,'Dreamers - Yongkang (永康門市)','台北市 ⋅ 大安區','taipei','10651台北市大安區信義路二段204號','Dongmen','https://goo.gl/maps/pKaYu6C29DpHkMbx7',25.033517876928016,121.5304436496725,'\"{\\\"mon\\\": \\\"7-22\\\", \\\"tue\\\": \\\"7-22\\\", \\\"wed\\\": \\\"7-22\\\", \\\"thu\\\": \\\"7-22\\\", \\\"fri\\\": \\\"7-22\\\", \\\"sat\\\": \\\"7-22\\\", \\\"sun\\\": \\\"7-22\\\"}\"',NULL,5,61,4,4,4,4,4,4,4,4,'yes',NULL,1,0,0,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://www.facebook.com/DreamersCoffeeRoasters/','https://www.instagram.com/dreamerscoffee_tw/','+886227771139',NULL,'\"[\\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/dreamers-coffee-roasters-yongkang/seating1.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/dreamers-coffee-roasters-yongkang/seating2.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/dreamers-coffee-roasters-yongkang/seating3.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/dreamers-coffee-roasters-yongkang/seating4.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/dreamers-coffee-roasters-yongkang/seating5.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/dreamers-coffee-roasters-yongkang/seating6.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/dreamers-coffee-roasters-yongkang/interior.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/dreamers-coffee-roasters-yongkang/drink.jpg\\\"]\"','\"{\\\"en\\\": \\\"A fairly new Dreamers location near Dongmen station. If you take the narrow staircase up to the 2nd floor you\'ll find a large seating area, with a large worktable and many small individual tables. The seats near the large windows have nice views and let in some natural light. On a weekday morning it was fairly quiet and not too busy.\\\\n\\\", \\\"zh-tw\\\": \\\"全新的Dreamers咖啡在東門站，從狹窄的樓梯往上走到二樓會來到很寬敞的座位區，依照慣例有很大個工作桌！(附有插座的工作桌幾乎是Dreamers的一大特色了)‵落地窗旁的位置更享有美好的自然光和景色，一個平日早晨通常滿安靜也不太擁擠。\\\\n\\\"}\"',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(51,'Dreamers - Fuxing (復興店)','台北','taipei','No. 7號, Lane 135, Section 1, Fuxing South Road, Da’an District, Taipei City, Taiwan 10666','Zhongxiao Fuxing','https://g.page/DreamersCoffeeRoastersFuxing?share',25.042762,121.544741,'\"{\\\"mon\\\": \\\"7-22\\\", \\\"tue\\\": \\\"7-22\\\", \\\"wed\\\": \\\"7-22\\\", \\\"thu\\\": \\\"7-22\\\", \\\"fri\\\": \\\"7-22\\\", \\\"sat\\\": \\\"7-22\\\", \\\"sun\\\": \\\"7-22\\\"}\"',NULL,1,1,3,3,2,4,3,4,3,4,'yes',NULL,1,0,0,0,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://www.facebook.com/DreamersCoffeeRoasters/','https://www.instagram.com/dreamerscoffee_tw/','+886227528229',NULL,'\"[]\"','\"null\"',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(52,'Ecole Cafe','台北','taipei','No. 6號, Lane 1, Qingtian Street, Da’an District, Taipei City, Taiwan 106','Dongmen','https://goo.gl/maps/UB9c3DcExBNuCpce6',25.02895512240559,121.5321639513991,'\"{\\\"mon\\\": \\\"9-19\\\", \\\"tue\\\": \\\"9-19\\\", \\\"wed\\\": \\\"9-18\\\", \\\"thu\\\": \\\"9-19\\\", \\\"fri\\\": \\\"9-19\\\", \\\"sat\\\": \\\"9-19\\\", \\\"sun\\\": \\\"9-19\\\"}\"',NULL,5,86,4,3,3,5,5,4,5,4,'yes',NULL,1,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://www.facebook.com/ecolecafe.cafetrouve/','https://www.instagram.com/ecole_cafe/','+886223222725',NULL,'\"[\\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/ecole-cafe/outside.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/ecole-cafe/seating1.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/ecole-cafe/seating2.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/ecole-cafe/seating3.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/ecole-cafe/seating4.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/ecole-cafe/seating5.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/ecole-cafe/interior.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/ecole-cafe/menu1.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/ecole-cafe/menu2.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/ecole-cafe/menu3.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/ecole-cafe/menu4.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/ecole-cafe/menu5.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/ecole-cafe/tea.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/ecole-cafe/food.jpg\\\"]\"','\"{\\\"en\\\": \\\"A quirky but cozy cafe with interesting decorations. The inside is quite large with plenty of seating options. I especially like the music selection, which was a mix of soft low-fi, piano, jazz, and instrumental music. The WiFi is great, the food/drinks options are really good (you can have a proper meal here), and the staff was very friendly. There are some drawbacks though. Most of the seats are hard and not very comfortable for extended stays, and some of the larger tables are lacking access to power outlets. In any case, it\'s nice to spend time here in the morning when it\'s very quiet, it got a little busy during lunch time though.\\\\n\\\", \\\"zh-tw\\\": \\\"一個妝點得很特別的咖啡店，裡頭空間很大，也有很多座位。我個人偏愛這裡的背景音樂，換搭著soft low-if、鋼琴、爵士以及其他伴奏。 WiFi很棒，食物也很好（你可以在這裡享用正餐），店員非常和善。\\\\n\\\\n小缺點是大部分的座位可能不適合久坐，大桌不太能搆到插座，不過這裡仍然很適合從早上待到中午，通常很安靜，直到午後才會熱鬧起來。\\\\n\\\"}\"',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(53,'Editor Books & Cafe','台北市 ⋅ 大安區','taipei','106台北市大安區溫州街24號','Taipower Building','https://g.page/editorsbookscafe?share',25.023320199200064,121.53318293978226,'\"{\\\"mon\\\": \\\"10:30-21\\\", \\\"tue\\\": \\\"10:30-21\\\", \\\"wed\\\": \\\"10:30-21\\\", \\\"thu\\\": \\\"10:30-21\\\", \\\"fri\\\": \\\"10:30-22\\\", \\\"sat\\\": \\\"10:30-22\\\", \\\"sun\\\": \\\"10:30-21\\\"}\"',NULL,3,10,4,5,4,4,4,3,4,5,'yes',NULL,1,0,0,1,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://www.facebook.com/editorsbookscafe/','https://www.instagram.com/editorsbookscafe/','+886223693333',NULL,'\"[\\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/editor-books-and-cafe/seating1.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/editor-books-and-cafe/seating2.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/editor-books-and-cafe/seating3.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/editor-books-and-cafe/interior.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/editor-books-and-cafe/outside.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/editor-books-and-cafe/tea.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/editor-books-and-cafe/menu1.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/editor-books-and-cafe/menu2.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/editor-books-and-cafe/menu3.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/editor-books-and-cafe/menu4.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/editor-books-and-cafe/sign.jpg\\\"]\"','\"{\\\"en\\\": \\\"A great cafe/bookshop for working, studying, or simply just to go read some books at. The atmosphere feels relaxed and quiet. The chairs are comfortable, and individual table lamps provide good lighting. There are several seats near the front of the shop, and another room in the back (which I didn\'t notice at first). I chose the seat by the window though, which was a great spot to spend the afternoon working from. Perhaps I was lucky, but the day I visited was very quiet, with many people either studying or working. The menu is quite large, with plenty of food and drinks. If you\'re looking to have a drink and a snack, the tea cake set was a great option.\\\\n\\\", \\\"zh-tw\\\": \\\"欒樹下書房是很適合讀書和工作的Cafe和書店，有很舒適的椅子，整個空間也很安靜，讓人感覺放鬆，個別座位的檯燈提供很好的照明。\\\\n\\\\n這裡大致分成前後兩個區塊，後方還有一個空間一開始比較不會注意到，我選擇了靠近窗戶的位置，這是一個能夠消磨一整個下午的好位置。也許我是幸運的，前往欒樹下書房拜訪的那天沒什麼人，其他訪客都很安靜的讀書或工作。\\\\n\\\\n值得一提的是這裡也有滿多餐點飲料可選，很推薦甜點和茶。\\\\n\\\\n—\\\\n雖然書店販售其他商品或餐飲常常為人詬病，覺得商業氣息削弱了書店的氛圍，但這也是讓一家好書店生存下去不得不為的一種選擇。很感謝這些書店仍然堅持著。\\\\n\\\"}\"',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(54,'ELEFUN café','台北','taipei','110, Taiwan, Taipei City, Xinyi District, 基隆路二段39巷4號','Taipei 101/World Trade Center','https://goo.gl/maps/56evM2YGd1W9gdZL9',25.0