ide.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/maven-coworking-cafe/downstairs.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/maven-coworking-cafe/seat.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/maven-coworking-cafe/coworking.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/maven-coworking-cafe/upstairs.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/maven-coworking-cafe/upstairs2.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/maven-coworking-cafe/tea.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/maven-coworking-cafe/menu1.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/maven-coworking-cafe/menu2.jpg\\\"]\"','\"{\\\"en\\\": \\\"A great place to work near Dazhi north of the Keelung River. The cafe feels very modern with a clean and minimal interior. The second floor is called the \\\\\\\"coworking space\\\\\\\" and has more seating and large worktables. Both floors are suitable for working and there is no extra fee to use the coworking space (minimum order 1 drink). The first floor was quite busy, even in the morning, but there were plenty of seats available upstairs. Both floors have very comfortable chairs, lots of power outlets, and fast WiFi. Good drink selection and some light food and snacks are available as well.\\\\n\\\", \\\"zh-tw\\\": \\\"基隆河北岸大直區域也有這麼一處適合工作的地方，裝潢簡單輕減。二樓開宗名義直接稱作「co-working space」—共享辦公室—任誰也不會錯用這個場所，座位很多也有適合幾個人一起工作的大辦公桌。其實無論一二樓都很適合遠端工作，有舒服的椅子，充足的插座和快速的WiFi體驗，並沒有額外的使用費（低消一杯飲料）。\\\\n\\\\n一樓可能比較繁忙，即使是一大早也有不少人，樓上通常有比較多空位。場所提供輕食和足夠的飲料選項。\\\\n\\\"}\"',NULL,NULL,NULL,'813224f9-10b0-477f-b68c-04347f7159c4'),(96,'MIDDLE NAME coffee & space','臺北市 ⋅ 大同區','taipei','No. 10號, Lane 18, Nanjing West Road, Datong District, Taipei City, 103','中山站','https://goo.gl/maps/fPijhJjyA1uYseWr8',25.0516392,121.52012,'\"{\\\"mon\\\": \\\"09:00 - 19:00\\\", \\\"tue\\\": \\\"09:00 - 19:00\\\", \\\"wed\\\": \\\"09:00 - 19:00\\\", \\\"thu\\\": \\\"09:00 - 19:00\\\", \\\"fri\\\": \\\"09:00 - 19:00\\\", \\\"sat\\\": \\\"10:00 - 20:00\\\", \\\"sun\\\": \\\"10:00 - 20:00\\\"}\"','',5,160,3.75,4,3.25,NULL,4,3.625,4,5,'yes','maybe',1,0,0,1,0,NULL,1,1,1,'https://www.facebook.com/middlenamecoffee','https://www.instagram.com/middlenamecoffee/','+886225566116','https://www.middlenamecoffee.com/','\"[\\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/middle-name-cafe/interior4.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/middle-name-cafe/seating1.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/middle-name-cafe/seating2.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/middle-name-cafe/seating3.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/middle-name-cafe/outside.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/middle-name-cafe/interior3.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/middle-name-cafe/sign.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/middle-name-cafe/menu1.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/middle-name-cafe/menu2.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/middle-name-cafe/coffee.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/middle-name-cafe/interior1.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/middle-name-cafe/interior2.jpg\\\"]\"','\"{\\\"en\\\": \\\"Definitely one of my favorite cafes near Zhongshan station. It\'s a great place to work from since it opens early, the WiFi is fast, and there are plenty of power outlets. I like the atmosphere since it feels very bright, airy, and modern, with plenty of natural light. The cafe is quite large, with many seating options available, but I normally choose the large work table (although I wish the chairs were a bit more comfortable). If you arrive in the morning it\'s usually very quiet and great for focusing on your work. Afternoons might be a little busy though.\\\\n<hr>\\\\nBright, modern cafe near Zhongshan with both counter, bar, and table seats available. Very fast wifi (160 Mb/s) and plenty of power outlets near the seats. The coldbrew coffee is quite strong as well. Came on a Tuesday and although quite full at times, there was always seating available.\\\\n\\\", \\\"zh-tw\\\": \\\"MIDDLE NAME這是中山區裡我到過的咖啡店中，我最喜歡的其中一家。主要原因是它開得早，很適合工作時間表比較規律的人，設備也很符合游牧工作的需求：WiFi很快、插座很多，另外這裡的視野非常開闊，大片玻璃帶進豐沛的太陽光，沒有太多的遮蔽使得室內空間也很明亮通風，裝潢更是特別時尚，有很多座位可選擇，我一般習慣坐在大工作桌邊(只希望椅子可以再舒服一點點)。\\\\n如果你來得早，這裡通常滿安靜，易於專心，下午人會比較多。\\\\n\\\"}\"',NULL,NULL,NULL,'b57008be-6170-464c-803f-902c6d088e54'),(97,'Milk Bar by BKA','台北','taipei','No. 6-1號, Lane 269, Section 3, Nanjing E Rd, Songshan District, Taipei City, Taiwan 105','Nanjing Fuxing','https://g.page/Milkbarbybka?share',25.052553,121.545712,'\"{\\\"mon\\\": \\\"13-21\\\", \\\"tue\\\": \\\"9-21\\\", \\\"wed\\\": \\\"9-21\\\", \\\"thu\\\": \\\"9-21\\\", \\\"fri\\\": \\\"9-21\\\", \\\"sat\\\": \\\"10-18\\\", \\\"sun\\\": \\\"10-18\\\"}\"',NULL,3,15,5,3,3,NULL,4,4,3,5,'yes',NULL,1,0,0,1,0,1,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://www.facebook.com/milkbarbybka','https://www.instagram.com/milkbarbybka/','+886227133118',NULL,'\"[\\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/milk-bar-by-bka/seating1.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/milk-bar-by-bka/seating2.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/milk-bar-by-bka/seating3.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/milk-bar-by-bka/logo.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/milk-bar-by-bka/outside.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/milk-bar-by-bka/tea.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/milk-bar-by-bka/menu.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r