taipei/ml-cafe/exterior.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/ml-cafe/menu1.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/ml-cafe/menu2.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/ml-cafe/menu3.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/ml-cafe/menu4.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/ml-cafe/menu5.jpg\\\"]\"','\"{\\\"en\\\": \\\"A popular lunch/brunch cafe near Dongmen station. During midday it can be a little busy/noisy. However, the afternoon was definitely quieter and made for a comfortable space to work from. The menu is large, with many food and drink options. There\'s WiFi, but it was very unstable during my visit. Also note that there is a 2 hour time limit during weekends.\\\\n\\\", \\\"zh-tw\\\": \\\"ML Cafe 東門附近很熱門的午餐/早午餐聖地，日中多半很熱鬧，下午則是安靜一點，空間也很舒適，非常適合工作。餐點和飲品的選擇都很豐富，適合待上一段時間不用擔心肚子餓。\\\\n\\\\n這裡有WiFi，不過在我前往時WiFi有點不穩定。另外需注意假日有兩小時的時間限制。\\\\n\\\"}\"',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(104,'Moi Cafe','臺北市 ⋅ 大同區','taipei','106台北市大安區仁愛路四段408巷13號','Sun Yat-Sen Memorial Hall','https://goo.gl/maps/ZpCEdxeghndLAZQu7',25.049308,121.5171935,'\"{\\\"mon\\\": \\\"11:00 - 21:30\\\", \\\"tue\\\": \\\"11:00 - 21:30\\\", \\\"wed\\\": \\\"11:00 - 21:30\\\", \\\"thu\\\": \\\"11:00 - 21:30\\\", \\\"fri\\\": \\\"11:00 - 21:30\\\", \\\"sat\\\": \\\"11:00 - 21:30\\\", \\\"sun\\\": \\\"11:00 - 21:30\\\"}\"','',4,35,4,5,4,NULL,3,4,3,4,'no','maybe',NULL,0,NULL,0,NULL,0,1,1,1,'https://www.facebook.com/Moi-cafe-%E4%BB%81%E6%84%9B%E5%BA%97-1591715957777576/','https://www.instagram.com/renai_moicafe/','+886227040099','','\"[\\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/moi-cafe/seating1.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/moi-cafe/seating2.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/moi-cafe/seating3.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/moi-cafe/seati