RT, which is quite a big inconvenience. The seats furthest in overlooking the big intersection have a nice view.\\\\n\\\", \\\"zh-tw\\\": \\\"其實我們還滿常去星巴克市政府站的，因為太容易去了，而且幾乎是時常爆滿，總覺得為何而寫，所以一直都沒有動筆。第一次來的人只要知道找到統一時代戶外的手扶梯上二樓，不要像我一樣繞了一大圈才找到了 :P。這裡最大的缺點就是沒有廁所，必須到百貨公司或捷運使用，非常不方便，不過如果能一早來佔到面向大十字路口的位置就是勝利，在這裡看人群和車潮川流是件非常有趣的事，就像在涉谷的十字路口上方一樣。\\\\n\\\"}\"',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(141,'STARBUCKS HanZhong','台北市 ⋅ 萬華區','taipei','108台北市萬華區漢中街51號','Ximen','https://goo.gl/maps/4vdFggv88CDcM7Fw6',25.044047228072458,121.50741468804024,'\"{\\\"mon\\\": \\\"8-22\\\", \\\"tue\\\": \\\"8-22\\\", \\\"wed\\\": \\\"8-22\\\", \\\"thu\\\": \\\"8-22\\\", \\\"fri\\\": \\\"8-22\\\", \\\"sat\\\": \\\"8-22:30\\\", \\\"sun\\\": \\\"8-22:30\\\"}\"',NULL,4,78,4,3,2,3,4,2,3,3,'',NULL,1,0,1,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://www.facebook.com/starbuckstaiwan','https://www.instagram.com/starbuckstw/','+886223705893','http://www.starbucks.com.tw/','\"[]\"','\"null\"',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(142,'STARBUCKS Houshanpi','台北','taipei','No. 968號, Section 5 of Zhongxiao East RoadSection 5 of Zhongxiao E Rd, Nangang District, Taipei City, 115025','Houshanpi','https://goo.gl/maps/C4vj8g3evxkGyEN66',25.044284414786354,121.58217957921724,'\"{\\\"mon\\\": \\\"7:30-21\\\", \\\"tue\\\": \\\"7:30-21\\\", \\\"wed\\\": \\\"7:30-21\\\", \\\"thu\\\": \\\"7:30-21\\\", \\\"fri\\\": \\\"7:30-21\\\", \\\"sat\\\": \\\"7:30-21\\\", \\\"sun\\\": \\\"7:30-21\\\"}\"',NULL,5,85,4,4,4,3,4,3,5,5,'yes',NULL,1,0,0,1,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://www.facebook.com/starbuckstaiwan','https://www.instagram.com/starbuckstw/','+886226538532','https://www.starbucks.com.tw/home/index.jspx','\"[\\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/starbucks-houshanpi/entrance.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/starbucks-houshanpi/interior.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/starbucks-houshanpi/seating1.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/starbucks-houshanpi/seating2.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/starbucks-houshanpi/seating3.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/starbucks-houshanpi/seating4.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/starbucks-houshanpi/seating5.jpg\\\"]\"','\"{\\\"en\\\": \\\"A great new Starbucks branch by Houshanpi MRT station. There are two floors, with the second featuring plenty of comfortable seating, a large work table, and even an outdoor balcony. The balcony unfortunately seems to be closed during the winter months though. The second floor is usually very quiet with most people working or studying. Weekdays, especially mornings, aren\'t too busy. Lots of power outlets and solid WiFi.\\\\n\\\", \\\"zh-tw\\\": \\\"星巴克近期在捷運後山埤捷運站拓點了！在二號出口附近，地理位置非常方便，這是一間非常適合工作的分店，有兩層樓，二樓有不少座位、工作桌、甚至還有一個陽台，可惜這個陽台冬天好像會關閉。二樓在假日經常客滿，許多人在這裡讀書工作，通常滿安靜的，平日早上通常滿空的，除此之外這裡也有很好的插座和Wifi。\\\\n\\\"}\"',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(143,'Starbucks Miramar','台北','taipei','104, Taiwan, Taipei City, Zhongshan District, Jingye 3rd Road, 20號1樓','Jiannan Rd','https://goo.gl/maps/fGTc3G9eG1JH6nPP8',25.083612,121.556707,'\"{\\\"mon\\\": \\\"8:30-23\\\", \\\"tue\\\": \\\"8:30-23\\\", \\\"wed\\\": \\\"8:30-23\\\", \\\"thu\\\": \\\"8:30-23\\\", \\\"fri\\\": \\\"8:30-23\\\", \\\"sat\\\": \\\"8:30-23\\\", \\\"sun\\\": \\\"8:30-23\\\"}\"',NULL,1,2,3,2,2,3,4,3,3,NULL,'maybe',NULL,1,0,0,1,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://www.facebook.com/starbuckstaiwan','https://www.instagram.com/starbuckstw/','+886221753190','http://www.starbucks.com.tw/','\"[]\"','\"null\"',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(144,'Starbucks Songshan','台北','taipei','No. 11號, Songshan Rd, Xinyi District, Taipei City, Taiwan 110','Songshan','https://goo.gl/maps/iWbiYjFj6PMQCSw36',25.0491,121.578814,'\"{\\\"mon\\\": \\\"7-22\\\", \\\"tue\\\": \\\"7-22\\\", \\\"wed\\\": \\\"7-22\\\", \\\"thu\\\": \\\"7-22\\\", \\\"fri\\\": \\\"7-22\\\", \\\"sat\\\": \\\"8-22\\\", \\\"sun\\\": \\\"8-22\\\"}\"',NULL,1,