at\\\": \\\"13-17:30\\\", \\\"sun\\\": \\\"13-17:30\\\", \\\"tue\\\": \\\"未營業\\\"}\"','',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'','\"[]\"','\"null\"',NULL,NULL,NULL,'837eee3e-d2fa-4ffa-af33-b58ce3f82b07'),(149,'STONE Workplace','台北','taipei','110, Taiwan, Taipei City, Xinyi District, Section 1, Keelung Rd, 141號2樓','Taipei City Hall','https://g.page/stoneworkplace?share',25.043046,121.565816,'\"{\\\"mon\\\": \\\"9-18\\\", \\\"tue\\\": \\\"9-18\\\", \\\"wed\\\": \\\"9-18\\\", \\\"thu\\\": \\\"9-18\\\", \\\"fri\\\": \\\"9-18\\\", \\\"sat\\\": \\\"未營業\\\", \\\"sun\\\": \\\"未營業\\\"}\"',NULL,5,250,5,4,4,0,2,3,5,2,'yes',NULL,1,0,1,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://www.facebook.com/stoneworkplace','https://www.instagram.com/stoneworkplace/','+886237621355','https://www.stoneworkplace.com/','\"[\\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/stone-workplace/seating1.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/stone-workplace/seating2.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/stone-workplace/seating4.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/stone-workplace/seating3.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/stone-workplace/booth.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/stone-workplace/meeting.jpg\\\"]\"','\"{\\\"en\\\": \\\"A fairly new co-working space close to Taipei City Hall. The interior is nice and well designed with plenty of natural light. There are several large worktables for flex members. As a flex member you pay a very reasonable price per day that you visit, rather than a fixed monthly fee. Day passes are sold in batches of 10. Tea/coffee is included. Great WiFi and plenty of power outlets. There\'s also a meeting room, phone booth, and several other seating areas for relaxing and taking phone calls. All the staff members are extremely friendly!\\\\n\\\", \\\"zh-tw\\\": \\\"這是一家位於台北市政府附近、剛成立不久的共享辦公室。裝潢新穎高雅，優秀的窗戶配置讓室內充滿自然光源，空間裡配置著幾張非常適合工作的大工作桌。只要註冊會員並購買以十天為一組的使用券，就能用非常合理的價格使用辦公空間及享用免費的茶和咖啡。和其他需要負擔固定月費及要求簽署長約的共享空間相比，這裡保留了更多的彈性。\\\\n\\\\nWiFi優秀、充電座充足。另外也提供會議室（需付費）、電話小間及其他休閒座位區，方便con-call和處理外務。所有的服務人員都非常親切和善！\\\\n＊費用相關內容可能變更，請直接與Stone workplace 洽詢＊\\\\n\\\"}\"',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(150,'Stoppage Time','台北市 ⋅ 大安區','taipei','106台北市大安區和平東路二段96巷15弄30號','Technology Building','https://goo.gl/maps/j1hqjqm1Pgofi5KG9',25.023268744779006,121.54227775803662,'\"{\\\"mon\\\": \\\"11-22\\\", \\\"tue\\\": \\\"11-22\\\", \\\"wed\\\": \\\"11-22\\\", \\\"thu\\\": \\\"11-22\\\", \\\"fri\\\": \\\"11-22\\\", \\\"sat\\\": \\\"11-22\\\", \\\"sun\\\": \\\"11-22\\\"}\"',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'\"[]\"','\"null\"',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(151,'Street No 6 街口6號珈啡','台北市 ⋅ 萬華區','taipei','108台北市萬華區貴陽街二段6號','Ximen','https://g.page/streetno6cafe?share',25.039246096447638,121.50677785792446,'\"{\\\"mon\\\": \\\"13-20\\\", \\\"wed\\\": \\\"13-20\\\", \\\"thu\\\": \\\"13-20\\\", \\\"fri\\\": \\\"13-20\\\", \\\"sat\\\": \\\"13-20\\\", \\\"sun\\\": \\\"13-20\\\", \\\"tue\\\": \\\"未營業\\\"}\"',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'\"[]\"','\"null\"',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(152,'SWELL CO. CAFE','台北','taipei','No. 23, Siwei Road, Da’an District, Taipei City, Taiwan 106','Daan, Zhongxiao Fuxing','https://goo.gl/maps/nbAsMHe9UVQP3kf59',25.035586,121.548157,'\"{\\\"mon\\\": \\\"11-19:30\\\", \\\"tue\\\": \\\"11-19:30\\\", \\\"wed\\\": \\\"11-19:30\\\", \\\"thu\\\": \\\"11-19:30\\\", \\\"fri\\\": \\\"11-19:30\\\", \\\"sat\\\": \\\"11-19:30\\\", \\\"sun\\\": \\\"11-19:30\\\"}\"',NULL,5,200,4,3,4,5,5,2,5,5,'yes',NULL,1,0,0,0,1,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://www.facebook.com/SWELL-CO-CAFE-1008869809231731/','https://www.instagram.com/swellcocafe/','+886227003003',NULL,