the-normal/seating5.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/the-normal/exterior.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/the-normal/food.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/the-normal/interior.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/the-normal/menu1.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/the-normal/menu2.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/the-normal/menu3.jpg\\\"]\"','\"{\\\"en\\\": \\\"Another great cafe near Nanjing Fuxing station. The interior is quite large and has a nice modern vibe. There are several seating areas, and one large worktable suitable for working with a group of people. Very fast WiFi, power outlets, and decent selection of food and drinks. I can definitely recommend trying the German pork sandwich with Sourdough bread.\\\\n\\\", \\\"zh-tw\\\": \\\"The Normal市另一間在南京復興站附近適合工作的咖啡廳，具有所有適合工作的條件：空間很開闊且有很多座位，也有很大的工作桌給多人討論使用。除此之外WiFi也非常快、有插座，餐點的選擇也不錯，很推薦他們的德國酸麵包火腿三明治。\\\\n\\\"}\"',NULL,NULL,NULL,'4d8109a4-54b1-4636-95fe-45512a953e3b'),(158,'Three Leafs Tea [三叶]','台北','taipei','1樓, No. 15號, Lane 295, Section 1, Fuxing South Road, Da’an District, Taipei City, Taiwan 106','Daan','https://goo.gl/maps/4YQYev6oJeaAuziq8',25.035206569892956,121.54459959760804,'\"{\\\"mon\\\": \\\"11-19\\\", \\\"tue\\\": \\\"11-19\\\", \\\"wed\\\": \\\"11-19\\\", \\\"thu\\\": \\\"11-19\\\", \\\"fri\\\": \\\"11-19\\\", \\\"sat\\\": \\\"11-19\\\", \\\"sun\\\": \\\"11-19\\\"}\"',NULL,5,280,4,3,3,3,3,3,3,5,'yes',NULL,0,0,0,0,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://www.facebook.com/3leafstea/','https://www.instagram.com/3leafstea/','+886227035851','http://www.3leafstea.com/','\"[\\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/three-leafs-tea/outside.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/three-leafs-tea/seating.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/three-leafs-tea/worktable.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/three-leafs-tea/table.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/three-leafs-tea/menu.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/three-leafs-tea/interior.jpg\\\"]\"','\"{\\\"en\\\": \\\"A combined tea shop and cafe that feels bright and modern. It\'s a good place for large groups since there are 3 large worktables (as well as some smaller tables). The WiFi is fast, and most of the tables have access to power outlets, but the chairs are not the most comfortable though. The menu is small, but the selection for both food and drinks is still quite good.\\\\n\\\", \\\"zh-tw\\\": \\\"[三叶]喫茶與咖啡兼備，裝潢明亮而現代。這裡有三張大工作桌，很適合多人團體一起工作，同時也有幾張小桌給個人使用。WiFi非常快，大部分桌子都有插座，只可惜椅子不算是最好坐的。菜單種類不多，但都很不錯。\\\\n\\\"}\"',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(159,'timeless 慕恆','台北市 ⋅ 大安區','taipei','106台北市大安區文昌街270號','Xinyi Anhe','https://goo.gl/maps/gBQToKjgF5Kw47mCA',25.032204141710917,121.55628444850299,'\"{\\\"mon\\\": \\\"8-21:30\\\", \\\"tue\\\": \\\"8-21:30\\\", \\\"wed\\\": \\\"8-21:30\\\", \\\"thu\\\": \\\"8-21:30\\\", \\\"fri\\\": \\\"8-21:30\\\", \\\"sat\\\": \\\"8-21:30\\\", \\\"sun\\\": \\\"8-21:30\\\"}\"',NULL,5,550,5,5,5,2,5,2,4,4,'yes',NULL,1,0,0,0,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://www.facebook.com/space.timeless','https://www.instagram.com/space.timeless/',NULL,'https://timeless.tw/','\"[\\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/timeless/seating1.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/timeless/interior1.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/timeless/seating2.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/timeless/seating3.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/timeless/seating4.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/timeless/seating5.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/timeless/seating6.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/timeless/interior2.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/timeless/snacks.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/timeless/sign.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/timeless/signup.jpg\\\"]\"','\"{\\\"en\\\": \\\"A new pay-to-use space that opened in Dec 2021. The space covers 3 floors, with the 2nd floor being the largest. Many seating areas (small and large tables). Drinks are included in the fee, and some small snacks are available for purchase. Sign-up process is super simple and the price is $150/2hr and a maximum of $450/day. Definitely reasonable for the occasional visit, but more expensive than a typical coworking space.\\\\n\\\\nThe space itself is nicely decorated, feels bright and modern, and quite comfortable. The WiFi is extremely fast and there are plenty of power outlets. The only downside I can see is that the space might get quite noisy if it\'s full, but so far it was very quiet.\\\\n\\\", \\\"zh-tw\\\": \\\"慕恆是一家十二月才剛開幕的新的付費辦公室，有三層樓，二樓是空間最大的，有比較多綜合的座位可以滿足不同的需求。收費的內容有包含飲料，也可以另外購買一些零食。\\\\n\\\\n註冊和使用方式都非常簡單！價格是150元兩小時，一天最高450元，絕對是非常合理的共享辦公室選擇，雖然費用也許稍微高於平均，但舒適度很高。\\\\n\\\\n作為一個共享辦公室，慕恆有很好的WiFi和許多插座，如上述所說，空間也足夠舒適，裝潢得也很時尚，唯一可以預期的缺點也許是當空間佔滿時可能會比較吵雜，但至少目前我還感受不到這個問題。\\\\n\\\"}\"',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(160,'To Dear (小路上藝文空間)','台北市 ⋅ 大安區','taipei','106台北市大安區羅斯福路二段77巷7號','Guting','https://goo.gl/maps/kxXy5cvZhwP8omQ18',25.026123138187653,121.52443418055518,'\"{\\\"tue\\\": \\\"11-20\\\", \\\"wed\\\": \\\"11-20\\\", \\\"thu\\\": \\\"11-20\\\", \\\"fri\\\": \\\"11-20\\\", \\\"sat\\\": \\\"11-20\\\", \\\"sun\\\": \\\"11-20\\\", \\\"mon\\\": \\\"未營業\\\"}\"',NULL,5,73,5,4,5,4,4,3,5,5,'yes',NULL,1,0,0,1,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://www.facebook.com/deardeer2012','https://www.instagram.com/deardeercafe/','+886223637768',NULL,'\"[\\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/to-dear/seating1.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/to-dear/seating2.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/to-dear/seating3.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/to-dear/seating4.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/to-dear/entrance.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/to-dear/menu.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/to-dear/outdoor.jpg\\\"]\"','\"{\\\"en\\\": \\\"A hidden gem near Guting MRT. The easiest way to access the cafe is to walk through the market area near Exit 4. The cafe itself has a very creatively decorated interior. I especially like the small details like the small plants in the tables. There\'s also a large outdoor seating area and apparently an art gallery as well. The best thing is that it was very quiet and very few people during the entire afternoon on a weekday, great for getting some focused work done. There\'s WiFi, power outlets, and a large menu with lots of tea. Furthermore the staff was very friendly and welcoming!\\\\n\\\", \\\"zh-tw\\\": \\\"小路上藝文空間是古亭站附近的隱藏好店，最容易抵達的方法是穿越四號出口旁的市場，入口非常可愛，就好像秘密花園的通道。\\\\n\\\\n這裡有非常嶄新的室內陳設，我特別喜歡讓一株植物穿透桌面的小巧思，除此之外這裡也有很大的戶外空間，和一個藝文展覽區。對我來說最好的是平日下午的氣氛很悠閒，沒有太多人，絕對適合專注。這裡有WiFi、插座、以及很豐富的茶類飲品可選，店員也非常親切熱情！\\\\n\\\"}\"',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(161,'Toast Chat','臺北市 ⋅ 大安區','taipei','106台北市大安區光復南路290巷58號','Sun Yat-Sen Memorial Hall','https://g.page/ToastChat?share',25.039492,121.5554933,'\"{\\\"mon\\\": \\\"12:00 - 22:00\\\", \\\"tue\\\": \\\"12:00 - 22:00\\\", \\\"wed\\\": \\\"未營業\\\", \\\"thu\\\": \\\"12:00 - 22:00\\\", \\\"fri\\\": \\\"12:00 - 22:00\\\", \\\"sat\\\": \\\"12:00 - 22:00\\\", \\\"sun\\\": \\\"12:00 - 22:00\\\"}\"','',5,83,3.5,3,3.5,4.5,4.5,3.25,4,3,'yes','no',1,0,0,0,1,1,1,1,1,'https://www.facebook.com/ToastChat/','https://www.instagram.com/toast_chat/','+886227215661'