://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/triangle-garden-cafe/seating4.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/triangle-garden-cafe/tea.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/triangle-garden-cafe/entrance.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/triangle-garden-cafe/menu1.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/triangle-garden-cafe/menu2.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/triangle-garden-cafe/menu3.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/triangle-garden-cafe/menu4.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/triangle-garden-cafe/menu5.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/triangle-garden-cafe/menu6.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/triangle-garden-cafe/menu7.jpg\\\"]\"','\"{\\\"en\\\": \\\"A very unique cafe, and if you\'re into Taiwanese tea then this is probably one of the better cafes in Taipei. The cafe is located on the second floor of an old building. You\'ll likely miss the tiny entrance if you aren\'t paying attention. The cafe space feels large and spacious, filled with old furniture and large wooden beams in the ceiling. It definitely has a special vibe!\\\\n\\\\nJust keep in mind, you\'ll probably want to make a reservation. There are only 3 small tables right by the entrance that are available without reservation (first come first serve), and most other tables are usually booked.\\\\n\\\", \\\"zh-tw\\\": \\\"角公園咖啡非常特別，如果你特別喜歡台灣茶，這裡會是你應該探索的地方。角公園隱藏在一處舊公寓的二樓，一不小心可能就錯過了。（這附近非常有趣，可以找到一些材料行和各式用具，適合在非假日一探究竟）\\\\n\\\\n角公園的空間很寬敞，環境很通風。家具的選擇搭配建物的屋齡都有些年紀，不過空間挑高，所以沒有壓迫的感覺，反而流露古典的風味。\\\\n\\\\n只是這裡非常熱門，一定要訂位，入口櫃檯旁邊保留了三張不用訂位的小桌，採先到先入座方式，但也非常熱門。\\\\n\\\"}\"',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(163,'Truffles Living (舒服生活)','台北','taipei','No. 66號, Wenchang Street, Da’an District, Taipei City, Taiwan 106','Xinyi Anhe','https://goo.gl/maps/hmGsUgqQBNQLF6qN9',25.032627,121.550854,'\"{\\\"mon\\\": \\\"11:30-19\\\", \\\"tue\\\": \\\"11:30-19\\\", \\\"wed\\\": \\\"11:30-19\\\", \\\"thu\\\": \\\"11:30-19\\\", \\\"fri\\\": \\\"11:30-19\\\", \\\"sat\\\": \\\"11:30-19\\\", \\\"sun\\\": \\\"11:30-19\\\"}\"',NULL,5,96,5,5,4,4,4,2,5,5,'yes',NULL,1,0,0,1,0,1,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://www.facebook.com/TrufflesLiving/','https://www.instagram.com/trufflesliving/','+886227088380',NULL,'\"[\\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/truffles-living/outside.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/truffles-living/seating1.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/truffles-living/seating2.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/truffles-living/seating3.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/truffles-living/seating4.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/truffles-living/menu1.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/truffles-living/menu2.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/truffles-living/menu3.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/truffles-living/menu4.jpg\\\"]\"','\"{\\\"en\\\": \\\"A quirky name and an odd description (\\\\\\\"bar restaurant furniture store\\\\\\\"). Despite this, it is in fact very work friendly and definitely worth visiting. The interior is rustic, filled with vintage and antique furniture. The atmosphere is calm, noise level is good, and it doesn\'t get very crowded throughout the day. The environment is clean and the space is quite large with multiple seating areas, including several large worktables. Most seats near the walls have power outlets. Friendly and very attentive staff. \\\\n\\\\nThe two main drawbacks are WiFi and price. The WiFi is usually very slow and difficult to use (even for light browsing). I find myself always using a mobile hotspot instead. Food and drinks are definitely on the pricey side. The quality is good, but the value is perhaps a little low. Also, some seats right under the AC can get a little cold.\\\\n\\\", \\\"zh-tw\\\": \\\"這家店有點奇妙，它有著古怪的名字和新奇的註解（酒吧餐廳與家飾店），但絕對是個值得探訪也適合工作的地方：裝潢古樸，陳設典雅，整個空間充滿復古的氛圍。「舒服生活」一般也不怎麼繁忙，噪音水準很低，大多時候非常寧靜。整體很乾淨且寬敞，有不同類型的座位因應不同需求，包含大工作桌，多數靠牆的座位都有插座。店員很殷勤體貼。\\\\n\\\\n只有兩點稍微令人卻步：WiFi和價格。WiFi很難連上也通常很慢（即使只是簡單瀏覽網頁），我發現我幾乎都需要用手機分享來支援我在筆電上的連線，食物和飲料絕對算是高價的，品質符合價位但CP值可能不這麼高。最後，冷氣口的位置可能有點冷。\\\\n\\\"}\"',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(164,'TSUTAYA BOOKSTORE','台北','taipei','115, Taiwan, Taipei City, Nangang District, Section 7, Zhongxiao East Road, 369號2F','Nangang','https://goo.gl/maps/Az5ZVUGu81wStN4y7',25.052982,121.606917,'\"{\\\"mon\\\": \\\"11-21:30\\\", \\\"tue\\\": \\\"11-21:30\\\", \\\"wed\\\": \\\"11-21:30\\\", \\\"thu\\\": \\\"11-21:30\\\", \\\"fri\\\": \\\"11-22\\\", \\\"sat\\\": \\\"11-22\\\", \\\"sun\\\": \\\"11-21:30\\\"}\"',NULL,4,50,3,3,4,3,4,5,5,4,'yes',NULL,1,0,1,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'+886227862869','http://www.citylink.tw/?p=8998','\"[\\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/tsutaya-bookstore/seating1.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/tsutaya-bookstore/seating2.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taipei/tsutaya-bookstore/seating3.jpg\\\"]\"','\"null\"',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(165,'Ueshima Coffee Bade Shop','台北市 ⋅ 松山區','taipei','105台北市松山區八德路三段32號','Taipei Arena','https://goo.gl/maps/wdFeqbckwvKVyJ2h8',25.04807049366343,121.55165611786072,'\"{\\\"mon\\\": \\\"7-21\\\", \\\"tue\\\": \\\"7-21\\\", \\\"wed\\\": \\\"7-21\\\", \\\"thu\\\": \\\"7-21\\\", \\\"fri\\\": \\\"7-21\\\", \\\"sat\\\": \\\"7:30-22\\\", \\\"sun\\\": \\\"7:30-21\\\"}\"',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'\"[]\"','\"null\"',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(166,'Ueshima Coffee Zh