ating5.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taiwan/coffee-wake-up/seating6.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taiwan/coffee-wake-up/seating7.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taiwan/coffee-wake-up/drink.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taiwan/coffee-wake-up/interior.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taiwan/coffee-wake-up/menu.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taiwan/coffee-wake-up/outside.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taiwan/coffee-wake-up/entrance.jpg\\\"]\"','\"{\\\"en\\\": \\\"During a trip to Kaohsiung I asked a friend for cafe recommendations. This was the first one he recommended, and it was definitely a great choice. The space is very large, feels modern and bright, with lots of natural light. There are plenty of seating options, and I especially liked the large worktables and the individual counter seats in the back (popular for working or studying).\\\\n\\\\nThe menu is quite cheap, and has both food and drink, so it\'s definitely suitable for a working brunch/lunch. I tried the bacon & peanut butter toast, which was quite good.\\\\n\\\\nThe WiFi was fast, there were plenty of power outlets. If I was living in Kaohsiung this would definitely be a regular spot!\\\\n\\\", \\\"zh-tw\\\": \\\"在高雄旅行的時候，我尋求朋友的推薦找到了「咖啡覺醒」，這是朋友第一個推薦的好店，實際體驗也發現所言非虛，這是一個非常好的選擇。咖啡覺醒的空間非常大，整體給人明亮時尚的感覺，有非常多的自然光線透進來。一如往常的，我非常熱愛大型工作桌，和在後頭的獨立吧檯型座位，最能讓人專心，除此之外他們也有很多種座位可以選，適合各種不同的用途。\\\\n\\\\n餐點價格算是非常便宜，同時也有供餐所以也是一個很好的早午餐場所，我點了培根和花生醬吐司，味道非常好！\\\\n\\\\n這裡的Wifi非常快，也有很多插座，如果我住在高雄的話，應該會非常常來這裡。\\\\n\\\"}\"',NULL,NULL,NULL,'188fb9f6-ec2e-4028-8cb3-6a273a2f88ed'),(183,'Enzo Cafe 安樓咖啡','基隆市 ⋅ 仁愛區','Keelung','200基隆市仁愛區仁三路11-3號',NULL,'https://goo.gl/maps/29GvNzuYN3PJ73hE9',25.128001670678856,121.74432169543213,'\"{\\\"mon\\\": \\\"11-19\\\", \\\"tue\\\": \\\"11-19\\\", \\\"wed\\\": \\\"11-19\\\", \\\"thu\\\": \\\"11-19\\\", \\\"fri\\\": \\\"11-19\\\", \\\"sat\\\": \\\"11-19\\\", \\\"sun\\\": \\\"11-19\\\"}\"',NULL,5,52,5,4,3,5,5,3,5,4,'yes',NULL,1,0,0,1,1,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://www.facebook.com/enzocafe.kl?locale=zh_TW','https://www.instagram.com/enzocafe.kl/','+886224250220',NULL,'\"[\\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taiwan/enzo/seating1.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taiwan/enzo/seating2.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taiwan/enzo/seating3.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taiwan/enzo/interior1.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taiwan/enzo/interior2.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taiwan/enzo/food.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taiwan/enzo/menu1.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taiwan/enzo/menu2.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taiwan/enzo/menu3.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taiwan/enzo/menu4.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taiwan/enzo/menu5.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taiwan/enzo/elevator.png\\\"]\"','\"{\\\"en\\\": \\\"A great work cafe in Keelung, close to the night market. From the outside this cafe looks very small, but if you take the slightly precarious stairs up to the second floor you\'ll find a nice seating area with thoughtful decorations. There\'s a large worktable and counter seats, great WiFi, plenty of power outlets, and comfortable seats. The space is comfortable, but can be a little noisy if the windows are open since you\'ll hear scooters driving by outside. There is a 2 hour if it\'s busy, but on a weekday this was not an issue.\\\\n\\\\nThe order system is quite interesting here! After you place your order downstairs the staff will hand you a buzzer, and they will send your order up to the second floor using the food elevator. When your buzzer beeps, open the elevator door, take out your order, place the buzzer inside the elevator, close the door, and then press the elevator button *once*.\\\\n\\\", \\\"zh-tw\\\": \\\"安樓咖啡這是一間位在基隆很靠近夜市的咖啡店，很適合工作。從外面來看這家店會覺得有點小，但爬上一道鐵梯之後就會來到寬敞的二樓，座位的安排很有規劃，這裡有很大的工作桌和吧檯座位，WiFi很好，也有很多插座和舒適的座椅，整個空間給人舒適的感覺。一些大家可能會在一的點：這裡可能會稍微有點噪音因為窗戶是開著的，有時會有機車通過的聲音。在比較繁忙的時候會有兩小時的時間限制但平日我想不太是個問題。\\\\n\\\\nPS：這裡的點餐方式滿好玩的！在一樓點完餐之後店員會給一個叫號器，就和許多店一樣，但這裡會用送餐電梯把餐點送上二樓，所以叫號器響的時候就可以打開電梯門拿取餐點，再直接把叫號器放進電梯按壓一下的下樓鍵即可。\\\\n\\\"}\"',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(184,'Heynuts 好堅果咖啡','台中','Taichung','No. 15號, Jingcheng 6th Street, West District, Taichung City, 403',NULL,'https://g.page/heynutscafe?share',24.155294284314838,120.65687372721702,'\"{\\\"mon\\\": \\\"9-21\\\", \\\"tue\\\": \\\"9-21\\\", \\\"wed\\\": \\\"9-21\\\", \\\"thu\\\": \\\"9-21\\\", \\\"fri\\\": \\\"9-21\\\", \\\"sat\\\": \\\"9-21\\\", \\\"sun\\\": \\\"9-21\\\"}\"',NULL,1,1.5,4,3,4,4,4,4,4,5,'maybe',NULL,1,0,0,1,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://www.facebook.com/heynutscafe/','https://www.instagram.com/heynutscafe/','+886423293210',NULL,'\"[\\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taiwan/heynuts/sign.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taiwan/heynuts/seating1.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taiwan/heynuts/seating3.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taiwan/heynuts/seating2.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taiwan/heynuts/seating4.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taiwan/heynuts/seating5.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taiwan/heynuts/interior.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taiwan/heynuts/menu1.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taiwan/heynuts/menu2.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taiwan/heynuts/menu3.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taiwan/heynuts/tea.jpg\\\"]\"','\"{\\\"en\\\": \\\"While spending some time in Taichung I found this cafe. On a weekday morning, the first floor was quite busy with people having brunch. However, if you go upstairs you\'ll find a large room, with lots of natural light, suitable for working. There\'s even a terrace if you feel like working outside. The menu is large, with lots of food and drink options. I\'m always happy when I can find a good milk tea without sugar. Overall I like the vibe of this cafe, but there is room for improvements. I wish the seats were more comfortable, there were more power outlets, and better WiFi.\\\\n\\\", \\\"zh-tw\\\": \\\"在台中溜達時，我意外發現了這家Cafe，即使那是個平常日的上午，一樓卻仍然早早滿座，許多人在這裡享用早午餐。上到二樓會發現還有一個很大的空間，採光充足，是個絕佳的工作環境，甚至還有一個很大的天台，可以邊工作邊曬曬太陽。\\\\n\\\\n好堅果咖啡的菜單應有盡有，能在一家Cafe找到品質好的無糖奶茶總是令我雀躍。我很喜歡這裡的氛圍，硬要挑骨頭的話，我希望椅子能夠更加舒適、以及有更多插座和穩定的WiFi。\\\\n\\\"}\"',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(185,'Homee Cafe 好饗咖啡','基隆市 ⋅ 中正區','Keelung','202基隆市中正區中正路1號1樓','Keelung','https://goo.gl/maps/6PDmRqqroxgiAsES8',25.131795127594348,121.7433473537186,'\"{\\\"mon\\\": \\\"8-17\\\", \\\"tue\\\": \\\"8-17\\\", \\\"wed\\\": \\\"8-17\\\", \\\"thu\\\": \\\"8-17\\\", \\\"fri\\\": \\\"8-17\\\", \\\"sat\\\": \\\"8-18\\\", \\\"sun\\\": \\\"8-18\\\"}\"',NULL,1,0.1,4,4,3,3,3,5,4,3,'yes',NULL,1,0,1,0,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,'http://www.facebook.com/Homee-Cafe-%E5%A5%BD%E9%A5%97%E5%92%96%E5%95%A1%E5%9F%BA%E9%9A%86%E6%B8%AF%E9%96%80%E5%B8%82-473245612827289/',NULL,'+886224275599','https://www.homeekitchen.com.tw/','\"[\\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taiwan/homee-cafe/seating1.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taiwan/homee-cafe/seating2.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taiwan/homee-cafe/entrance.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taiwan/homee-cafe/menu.jpg\\\"]\"','\"{\\\"en\\\": \\\"While visiting Keelung I was trying to find a place to get some work done in the morning on a weekday. Most cafes seem to open around lunch time, but this place opened earlier. The cafe is actually located inside the ferry terminal building. I was hoping to have some nice harbor views, but unfortunately it was blocked by the large cruise ship parked just outside. Plenty of seating, comfortable chairs, and power outlets. Unfortunately the WiFi was extremely slow, so you\'ll need to use a personal hot spot here.\\\\n\\\", \\\"zh-tw\\\": \\\"zh-tw: |\\\\n在基隆的時候，我試著去找一個地方可以讓我在平日早上快速完成工作，但是這裡大部分的咖啡店看起來都是午餐時間左右才開，只有「好響咖啡」開得比較早，好響咖啡其實位在基隆港務局裡面，有很多座位和舒適的椅子，也有一些插座，WiFi則是非常慢，所以可能要有心理準備要使用個人的數據分享。\\\\n\\\\n當天其實有點期待看到一些港口景觀，可惜的是到訪那天剛好有一艘很大的郵輪停在正前方，很好奇平常的視野是什麼樣子。\\\\n\\\"}\"',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(186,'innside coffee','屏東縣 ⋅ 恆春鎮','Pingtung','946屏東縣恆春鎮南灣路206號',NULL,'https://goo.gl/maps/gy4RH2tCCPiS6Vby6',21.96106888729446,120.76358136135767,'\"{\\\"mon\\\": \\\"11-19:30\\\", \\\"wed\\\": \\\"11-19:30\\\", \\\"thu\\\": \\\"11-19:30\\\", \\\"fri\\\": \\\"11-19:30\\\", \\\"sat\\\": \\\"11-19:30\\\", \\\"sun\\\": \\\"11-19:30\\\", \\\"tue\\\": \\\"未營業\\\"}\"',NULL,5,50,4,3,4,NULL,1,3,5,3,'yes',NULL,1,0,0,1,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://www.facebook.com/innside.coffee','http://instagram.com/innside_coffee','+88688880438',NULL,'\"[\\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taiwan/innside-coffee/seating1.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taiwan/innside-coffee/seating2.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taiwan/innside-coffee/seating3.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taiwan/innside-coffee/interior1.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taiwan/innside-coffee/menu1.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taiwan/innside-coffee/menu2.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taiwan/innside-coffee/menu3.jpg\\\", \\\"https://d2ltlh9sj9r3jz.cloudfront.net/cafe-seeker/taiwan/innside-coffee/out